<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="K_7356" type="Brief"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Giovanni Battista Pioda an Alfred Escher, Bern, Mittwoch, 30. Dezember 1863</title></titleStmt><publicationStmt><p>Digitale Briefedition Alfred Escher, Zürich: Alfred Escher-Stiftung.</p></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><msDesc><msIdentifier><institution>SBB Historic</institution><idno>VGB_GB_SBBGB02_003</idno></msIdentifier></msDesc></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><textClass><keywords scheme="http://briefedition.alfred-escher.ch/keywords"><term>Simplonbahnprojekt</term></keywords></textClass><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><persName key="Pioda Giovanni Battista" type="addressee">Giovanni Battista Pioda</persName><persName key="Escher (vom Glas) Alfred" type="sender">Alfred Escher</persName><placeName>Bern</placeName><date when="1863-12-30">30. Dezember 1863</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><placeName>Zürich</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="previous" target="B3506"/><ref type="next" target="B3504"/><ref type="next-in-corresp" target="B8402"/><ref type="previous-in-corresp" target="B7355"/></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><front>
      <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7356_p1"> <note type="com" xml:id="K_7356_c0">Nachträgliche Notiz unten links von dritter Hand: <orig>Obigen Band <choice><abbr>Hrn.</abbr><expan>Herrn</expan></choice> Baurath <persName key="Beckh August von">Beckh</persName> in <placeName key="Stuttgart (D)">Stuttgart</placeName> am <date when="1864-01-04">4. Januar 64.</date> übersandt.</orig> </note> <lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>
        <hi rend="printed">Schweizerische<lb xml:id="p1-l2"/>EIDGENOSSENSCHAFT
            <lb xml:id="p1-l3"/>DEPARTEMENT DES INNERN
            <lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>Bureau des Bauwesens.</hi>
      </p> 
      <div type="dateline">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7356_p2"><lb xml:id="p1-l5"/>
          <hi rend="printed">
            <placeName key="Bern (Stadt)">Bern</placeName>, den</hi>
          <date when="1863-12-30">30 Dezember <hi rend="printed">186</hi>3.</date>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7356_p3"><lb xml:id="p1-l6"/>Herrn Nationalrath <hi><choice><abbr>D<hi rend="sup">r</hi> </abbr><expan>Doktor / Doctor</expan></choice></hi> <hi>A. Escher</hi> <lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>in
            <lb xml:id="p1-l8"/><hi><placeName key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zürich</placeName></hi>.</p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="center" xml:id="K_7356_p4"><lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>Hochgeachteter Herr,</p>
      </div>
    </front><body>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7356_p5"><lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>In Ergänzung unserer Sendung
                <lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>vom <date when="1863-11-25">25<hi rend="sup">ten</hi> vorigen Monats</date> (Pläne
                <lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>der <placeName key="Simplon (Pass)">Simplon</placeName>bahn) beehren wir
                <lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>uns Ihnen mitfolgend noch zu über<lb xml:id="p1-l14" break="no"/>mitteln:
                <lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>1 <choice><abbr>Bd.</abbr><expan>Band</expan></choice> <hi> «Etudes de la traversée du <placeName key="Simplon (Pass)">Simplon</placeName> <lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>entre <placeName key="Brig-Glis">Gliss–Brigg</placeName> &amp; <placeName key="Domodossola (I)">Domo-d'Ossola</placeName> </hi>»
            </p>
    </body><back>
      <div type="closer">
        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7356_p6"><lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>Genehmigen Sie, Hochgeachteter Herr,
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>die erneuerte Versicherung unserer
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l19"/>vollkommenen Hochachtung!
                </p>
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7356_p7"><lb xml:id="p1-l20"/>
          <hi>Der Vorsteher</hi>
          <lb xml:id="p1-l21"/>des <choice><abbr>eidg.</abbr><expan>eidgenössisch / eidgenößisch</expan></choice> Departements des Innern</p>
      </div>
      <div type="signature">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7356_p8"><lb xml:id="p1-l22"/>J. B. Pioda
  </p>
      </div>
    </back></text></TEI>